item.title: Telangana: One student dead, two others injured in Jogulamba Gadwal
item.description:
<![CDATA[Telangana One Student Dead Two Others Injured In Jogulamba Gadwal
Telangana: One student dead, two others injured in Jogulamba Gadwal
The Bolero van hit the two-wheeler and the two-wheeler lost control, killing Murali on the spot and two others sustained injuries
By Telangana Today Published Date - 24 February 2025, 09:51 AM
Representational image
Jogulamba Gadwal: One student died and two others sustained injuries, when a Bolero van hit a two-wheeler at Shantinagar under Vaddepally mandal....]]>
item.author: Telangana Today
